 1вҶ’/**
 2вҶ’ * sequant run - Execute workflow for GitHub issues
 3вҶ’ *
 4вҶ’ * Orchestrator module that composes focused workflow modules:
 5вҶ’ * - worktree-manager: Worktree lifecycle (ensure, list, cleanup, changed files)
 6вҶ’ * - phase-executor: Phase execution with retry and failure handling
 7вҶ’ * - phase-mapper: Label-to-phase detection and workflow parsing
 8вҶ’ * - batch-executor: Batch execution, dependency sorting, issue logging
 9вҶ’ */
10вҶ’
