  5вҶ’ * from the run command so it can be reused by batch-executor
  6вҶ’ * and other consumers.
  7вҶ’ *
  8вҶ’ * @module phase-mapper
  9вҶ’ */
 10вҶ’
 11вҶ’import type { Phase } from "./types.js";
 12вҶ’
 13вҶ’/**
 14вҶ’ * Minimal options interface for phase mapping.
